Detailed Description

cvmx_nqm_vf::_sq::_ifc

NQM_VF(x)_SQ(0..16)_IFC are the submission queue inflight counts for function x. Includes both admin and IO queues. NQM_VF_MODE[VF_MODE] selects the queues and functions that are actually present in the hardware. See NQM_VF_MODE_E.
